### =========================
### 1️⃣ Alle Assets anzeigen
### =========================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets
Authorization: Basic admin@test.de password
Accept: application/json

### =========================
### 2️⃣ Asset zuweisen (ASSIGN)
### Rolle: ASSET_MANAGER
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/assets/802154207636508724/assign
Authorization: Basic manager@test.de password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personUuid": 802154207481319642
}

### =========================
### 3️⃣ Asset zurückgeben (RETURN)
### Rolle: ASSET_MANAGER
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/assets/802154207636508724/return
Authorization: Basic manager@test.de password

### =========================
### 4️⃣ Asset blockieren (BLOCK)
### Rolle: ADMIN
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/assets/802154207636508724/block
Authorization: Basic admin@test.de password

### =========================
### 5️⃣ Asset entblockieren (UNBLOCK)
### Rolle: ADMIN
### =========================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/assets/802154207636508724/unblock
Authorization: Basic admin@test.de password
